      "dateCreated": "2026-03-31",
      "description": "10X snMultiome (scRNA-seq + scATAC-seq) analysis pipeline for gastric cancer using Seurat and Signac. Reproduces the analysis from 'Epithelial WNT secretion drives niche escape of developing gastric cancer'. Includes QC, MACS2 peak calling, SCT integration, UMAP clustering, cell-type annotation, differential expression (MAST), differential accessibility, and JASPAR2020 motif enrichment for Wnt7+ vs Lgr5+ populations in wild-type and Kras-mutant mouse gastric tissue.",
